‘—ЩRarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/blog/2021-01-09-twin0072.mdЩ@c061bf92e508d903029b680562f1422003ad7bd18bb4df5e8b4ee050ff646595іThis week in Nu #72‘іThis week in Nu #72ЪЋjonathandturner improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2839] some errors
, improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2847] InputStream
, fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2849] variable scope leak
, added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2851] shadowing
, add support for 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2855] ``source``
 during parsing
, renamed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2859] set/set-env to let/let-env
, released 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2860] 0.25.0
, pinned 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2868] ``syn``
 to avoid build breakage
, removed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2887] the line primitive
, renamed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2889] Path and Pattern
, updated startup to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2890] treat all startup lines as coming from the same source
, and fixed 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2893] reading/writing of bigint/bigdecimal
JosephTLyons fixed a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2841] typo in the sorting error message
LhKipp added the 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2846] ability to use a comment above the custom command as part of its description
, improved 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2885] the precedence rules for 
``which``
jinlow added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2848] support for filesizes to 
``math median``
baoyachi 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2853] reduced the number of dependencies
, updated 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2861] shadow-rs
stormasm 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2854] refactoring some function in nu-cli
sousajf1 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2857] updated some dependencies
wycats 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2865] improved and documented the lexer
TrevorAC99 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/2880] updated rust-embed
fdncred created a new 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/vscode-nushell-lang] VSCode plugin for Nushell!
